==敘述==
[[File:Australovenator_Scale_V2.svg|thumb]]
如同其他[[大盜龍類|大盜龍類]]，南方獵龍是{{link-en|二足行動|Bipedalism}}的[[肉食性動物|肉食性動物]]。<ref name="HMC04">{{Cite book |title=The Dinosauria |url=https://archive.org/details/dinosauriandedit00weis |last=Holtz |first=Thomas R., Jr. |last2=Molnar |first2=Ralph E. |last3=Currie |first3=Philip J. |publisher=University of California Press |year=2004 |isbn=0-520-24209-2 |editor-last=Weishampel |editor-first=David B. |edition=2nd |location=Berkeley |pages=[https://archive.org/details/dinosauriandedit00weis/page/71 71]–110 |editor-last2=Dodson |editor-first2=Peter |editor-last3=Halszka  |editor-first3=Osmólska }}</ref>手臂強壯帶有大爪。<ref name="Hocknull-etal-2009"/>臀高2公尺、身長6公尺、體重約500至1000公斤。因為是種體格相對輕盈的掠食者，被形容為「牠那個時代的[[獵豹|獵豹]]」。<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.abc.net.au/news/stories/2009/07/03/2615874.htm |title=Scientists discover 3 new Aussie dinosaurs |last=Phillips |first=Nicky |date=2009-07-03 |work=ABC News |access-date=2018-01-11 |department=ABC Science Online |language=en-AU |archive-date=2011-05-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110501091820/http://www.abc.net.au/news/stories/2009/07/03/2615874.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>
